{
  "stem": "6900.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maurice-- Maurice will give you the date, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With my son?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My son.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] [SIGHS] I met my son in England before I went permanently back to-- to London, to England.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because while I was working, I-- that was afterwards-- I-- I used to go, like, for a weekend and see him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I'd see-- I met him before that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can imagine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can't describe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[SOBBING] I can't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because he'd already left Holland when I got to Holland in the first instant.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the first place, I took him back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the first instance, I took him back with me, and he didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought, well, I'm not leaving him now I've found him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he had a bicycle in Holland for one of his birthdays, with those wooden blocks, because he couldn't reach the pedals.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I thought, well, the only way, maybe, I'll get him to go with me is to buy him a new bicycle in London.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I bought him a Raleigh bicycle-- I have to tell you this, because it relates to later on-- and he still didn't want to go, but he did come back with me.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when we got back, the Diamond Group knew that we were back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because his father was so well liked, and everything, the Diamond Group decided they would take him as an apprentice, which is a three-year apprenticeship.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- you have to pay for that, but no money from me would they take-- I didn't have it in the first place-- would they take, because of what happened.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he went to work in the factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He hated it.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
